    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >this is the demo version in development of the game Slime Hero Broken Tower. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the role of a small slime on an epic journey through the Tower of Slimes. Immerse yourself in a world filled with diverse slimes and unique environments. With no prior knowledge, let the tower's caretaker guide you as you discover who you are and why you were created.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/446faa9473f96f2eeea38c4ae27fbc20.poster.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1152 height=648 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/446faa9473f96f2eeea38c4ae27fbc20.webm?t=1771033215\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a universe rich in interactions and stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/c178b15990afb8504966eaee736633b4.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress, learn new abilities: shoot fireballs, stick to walls, and master the powers of the elements scattered throughout the tower — fire, ice, earth, plant, lightning, and poison — each with its own unique characteristics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/edc43a6f9fc3e0431be70cf5c3fa323c.avif?t=1771033215\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras_big/edc43a6f9fc3e0431be70cf5c3fa323c.avif?t=1771033215 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the mysteries within the Tower of Slimes, a place transformed by its inhabitants. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/8755e886d9ca252f028b2cc8aa050327.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover unique landscapes with specific mechanics for each map, find hidden locations, and engage in special interactions. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/988fa94f307c6c038b72d21e34d469fe.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create your own story with meaningful choices, conversing with NPCs of each element. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/6d2100e5bcb4f61207258eca3e687460.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With your adaptive abilities, face challenging bosses and various enemies. Survive battles, grow stronger, and unveil the secrets of this fascinating world. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3146230/extras/96de0944f72cb45faba721ae8caff06c.avif?t=1771033215\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p>",
